    PROCEDURE Table3@2001();
    VAR
      B3@1000 : Record 3;
    BEGIN
      A3.CHANGECOMPANY(F.GetCompanyName);
      B3.CHANGECOMPANY(F.GetCompanyName);
      F.UpdateKey(A3.CURRENTKEY);
      A3.MARKEDONLY := F.Modify;
      IF A3.FIND('-') THEN
        REPEAT
          B3 := A3;
          B3.SETRECFILTER;
          F.Update(B3.GETFILTERS);
          F.CheckCode(B3.FIELDNO("Code"),B3.FIELDNAME("Code"),MAXSTRLEN(B3."Code"),B3."Code");
          F.CheckDecimal(B3.FIELDNAME("Discount %"),B3."Discount %");
          F.CheckText(B3.FIELDNAME("Description"),MAXSTRLEN(B3."Description"),B3."Description");
          IF F.Modify THEN BEGIN
            A3.DELETE;
            B3.INSERT;
          END ELSE
            IF NOT A3.MARK THEN
              A3.MARK := F.Mark;
        UNTIL A3.NEXT = 0;
    END;
    PROCEDURE Table4@2002();
    VAR
      B4@1000 : Record 4;
    BEGIN
      A4.CHANGECOMPANY(F.GetCompanyName);
      B4.CHANGECOMPANY(F.GetCompanyName);
      F.UpdateKey(A4.CURRENTKEY);
      A4.MARKEDONLY := F.Modify;
      IF A4.FIND('-') THEN
        REPEAT

          B4.SETRECFILTER;
